    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3463" key="#Princeps">Radelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langubardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3686" key="#childOf">Ursi</persName> dilecti filii
                        nostri, vobis <persName ref="#people/3663" key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            >Gaydenardo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldo</rs> nostro <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >curtem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Palatium">sacri nostri palatii</rs> in <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property"
                            ref="#places/3444">Mataloni</placeName> quas ante hos dies <name
                            ref="Landulfus">Landulfi</name>
                        <rs key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Outflow">concessa habuimus</rs>,
                        predicta vero curte <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation">pro merito culpe
                            eius ad nostras rediit potestates</rs>, et concessimus tibi prephato
                        vineas et terras, servos et ancillas et cum omnia sua pertinentia, in ea
                        videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum
                        predicta <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ><rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> cum <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs> et
                                <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> seu <rs key="#Slave"
                                >servis et ancillis</rs> et cum omnibus suis pertinentibus</rs> in
                        integrum vos et heredes vestri habere et possidere valeatis, et a nullo ex
                        nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldis vel a quibuscumque agentibus
                        habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod
                        vero preceptus concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego
                            <persName ref="#people/3462" key="#Writer">Theodericus</persName>. Actus
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName>
                        secundo anno, mense magio, quarta indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
